{"tid":2226076,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"港人前路｜美公佈2021年度難民接收計劃  香港首次納入特殊分配項目","createTime":"2020-10-01T19:08:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-02T05:44:38.000Z","uid":239336,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e4c4ca1e62f4039f44d1c808620277ecb1b3079d","tid":2226076,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T19:08:25.000Z","msg":"美國國務院周三發表聲明，宣布在10月1日開始的2021財政年度，計劃接收15000名難民，香港更被首次納入難民分配項目類別，與伊拉克、薩爾瓦多、危地馬拉、洪都拉斯、古巴和委內瑞拉歸於同一類。<br />\n<br />\n國務院的聲明說，美國預期在2021年財政年度接收超過30萬名新難民和尋求庇護者，其中15000名屬美國難民接收計劃的難民，另外逾29萬為尋求庇護人士。<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普7月中簽署了名為「香港正常化」（Hong Kong Normalization）的總統行政命令，指在港版國安法之下，港人可能因為被中國指為分裂或顛覆國家面臨終身監禁，要求美國政府各部門，就有關涉及香港的法例進行修訂，當中包括重新分配難民限額予港人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201002/ZKSWJ44XVBFM5GO4HX4U45RJMY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201002%2FZKSWJ44XVBFM5GO4HX4U45RJMY%2F&d=NeqW8uJC54Uj1%2BY3pyrdAife5Xzx4ME6JwL9AZsFK0I%3D&h=c75ab495\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201002%2FZKSWJ44XVBFM5GO4HX4U45RJMY%2F&h=8d7edfff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201002/ZKSWJ44XVBFM5GO4HX4U45RJMY/</a>"},{"pid":"4b5e765e5a3be48924b80a0f488f47ff82ccb128","tid":2226076,"uid":239336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T19:11:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b81cf03cfe24ce59db28241e0fbb0661274b68a5","tid":2226076,"uid":199768,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T20:29:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5758cccabc95fa7c7bd5ab3d32ba5f32fdd32b8d","tid":22